==Serbian==

===Phrase===
'''[[Ваистину]] [[се]] [[роди]]'''

# [[Merry Christmas]] (''greeting'')
# (''literally''): [[verily|Verily]], [[Jesus|he]] [[has]] [[been]] [[born]].

===Usage notes===
This is only the '''reply''' part of the greeting.  The ''greeting'' part preceding the reply is [[Христос се роди#Serbian|Христос се роди]].''

====Latin/Roman spelling====
*[[Vaistinu se rodi#Serbian|Vaistinu se rodi]]

